Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi boleh saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.77,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.10,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak boleh pokoknya...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan dilihat, Nona cantik yang di sana.
