Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.14,0:07:58.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.33,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Nona tercantik di dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.04,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengetahuinya juga.
