Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Walaupun musim panas sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.11,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Keperjakaan kita masih belum berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.11,0:13:41.80,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hyoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.61,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.91,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kita akan menjadi orang dewasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.17,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Memesona.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.57,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ke dunia para orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.01,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.70,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.51,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.07,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai kapan akan berlanjut?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.10,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?\NPerkelahian lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Saat orang terkena musibah...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.00,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini sudah tidak ada tamu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.07,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Larilah jika tidak ingin mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.74,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Amukan akan dimulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.20,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Amukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bulannya merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.50,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.11,0:15:04.91,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.57,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.54,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Larilah jika tidak ingin mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Amukan akan dimulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bulannya merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.77,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.37,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Di luar, mayat hidupnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.31,0:15:31.34,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.91,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tadi Tuan Shadow yang melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.31,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Shadow?\NMaksudmu Shadow yang itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.27,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Pemeran utama yang bertindak seenaknya\Nterhadap gereja busuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.11,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sama bahayanya\Ndengan para penguasa di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.40,Italic,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Orang itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.14,Italic,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin orang jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan, Marie?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.34,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melarikan diri dari kota gila ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.61,0:16:04.86,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau berencana berlari?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.57,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tak akan berakhir baik\Njika kau ketahuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.87,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Mas Shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.34,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Jika bisa lari, larilah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.31,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Jika nasibmu baik,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.31,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}pasti ada jalannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.87,0:16:24.14,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tidak pernah ada yang berhasil kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.50,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Yukime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Para vampir\Nmenyebarkan mayat hidup ke kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.07,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.07,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Cid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.74,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ini karena aku membawamu\Nke tempat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.07,0:16:49.41,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kau yang sedang mencari\Nanak berambut dan bermata hitam?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sebelumnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menemukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.54,0:16:55.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adikku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sudah menemukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.17,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mayat itu bukan anak bermata\Ndan berambut hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.67,0:17:02.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.60,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa lu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.03,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasar perkataanmu,\Naku memiliki dua orang yang muncul di kepalaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Yang pertama aku melihatnya\Nsaat bulan mulai memerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tersenyum di depan mayat hidup\Nyang mengamuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.94,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, adikku tidak mungkin tersenyum\Njika dia dalam ketakutan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.04,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kedua, aku melihatnya tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.14,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah kesatria pedang sihir\Ntanpa keunikan sama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.64,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana?\NBeri tahu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.31,0:17:30.20,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihatnya saat sedang dibawa\Noleh bawahan Ratu Darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.61,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ratu Darah...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.34,Atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Di bawa ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.31,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Menara Merah?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.11,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Adikmu dibawa ke tempat\Ndi mana Ratu Darah berada.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.81,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berada di Menara Merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.00,0:17:46.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Karena para vampir sedang berusaha\Nmenjadikan dia persembahan untuk Ratu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.74,0:17:47.54,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Persembahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.94,0:17:51.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Saat Ratu Darah Elisabeth akan bangkit\Ndari tidurnya dalam 1.000 tahun sekali,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.24,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}membutuhkan darah dari lelaki muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.34,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Info dari mana bahwa Ratu\Nakan terbangun dari tidurnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menyembunyikan itu dan menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.07,0:18:01.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Selama 1.000 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.40,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Menunggu malam yang akan\Nmemberikan para vampir kekuatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Menunggu malam\Ndi mana bulan merah akan datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.24,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Memang benar\Nakhir-akhir ini bulan terlihat merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.87,0:18:15.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bulan merah juga memberikan efek\Nkepada Ratu yang sedang tertidur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada persembahan\Nsebagai bentuk pemanggilan, pasti...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.24,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin Cid ada di menara itu, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mereka butuhkan darah orang hidup,\Nberarti dia masih hidup, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.74,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuanku adalah Ratu Darah Elisabeth.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perlu untuk pergi ke Menara Merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.00,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya kita memiliki\Ntempat tujuan yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.21,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita bekerja sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.68,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Etto...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.40,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.37,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Pemburu vampir.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.00,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Claire.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.70,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat sulit untuk masuk melalui jalan depan,\Ntapi aku ada cara.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ikuti aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.01,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu aku, Cid.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mati, kita akan mati.\NMati isih perjaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.67,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak lucu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.17,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku belum pernah dicium seseorang\Nselain oleh ibuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.54,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hyoro, aku tidak akan melupakan jasamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tunggu cok!\NJangan tinggalkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.80,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}{(\fad(0,111)\fscx99\fscy99\t(\fscx151\fscy151)}Tetek!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.27,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Juggernaut?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.07,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aroma perang besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.04,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti ini terakhir kali terjadi\Nsaat para monster menyerang, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.27,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah saatnya, mundur!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.10,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Larilah lewat atap sampai ke stasiun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.90,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kalian lakukan seenaknya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.37,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini apa kalian masih\Nkesatria pedang sihir gereja?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli dengan reputasi kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.80,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan seperti ini tidak menguntungkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.71,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar tukang mulung.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.31,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua, bagian depan sudah tidak bisa lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.64,0:19:50.44,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Larilah jika tidak ingin mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.10,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Amukan akan dimulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.90,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.50,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Dia, yang ada di selebaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Bulannya merah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.14,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya sedikit waktu yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.37,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Crimson.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.00,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar lagi persiapan untuk persembahan\Nakan selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.24,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Kendali terhadap kota pun sesuai rencana.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.24,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.24,0:20:25.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perlawanan yang tidak terduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.47,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Palingan hanya mereka, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.97,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Para orang bodoh\Nyang lancang merasa setara denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.04,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan dari Menara Putih, Youko Yukime.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.64,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan dari Menara Hitam, Juggernaut.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.10,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Biarkan mereka sesukanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.84,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka akan berakhir\Nbersamaan dengan kembalinya Ratu Darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.24,0:20:48.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.88,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ada seorang lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.88,0:20:51.62,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.94,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Ada seseorang\Nyang membunuh para mayat hidup di kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.30,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Orang lemah mundurlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.00,Utama,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(00,40)}Mati sana, rubah!
